## Usage

<!-- GUIDANCE: Show exactly how to use this prompt. Concrete is better than general. -->

### As a System Prompt

Paste the System Prompt section into your Claude Code system prompt or project CLAUDE.md:

```markdown
## Context
[Paste system prompt here with variables substituted]
```

### Customizing Variables

To customize for your use case, replace variables before pasting:

**Example — for marketing writers:**
```
{{AUDIENCE}} → "non-technical marketing managers"
{{FORMAT}} → "bullet points with headers"
{{TONE}} → "enthusiastic and jargon-free"
```

### Selecting a Variant

| Variant | Use When | File |
|---------|---------|------|
| Concise | Quick output, limited context | `variants/concise.md` |
| Detailed | Thorough output, full context | `variants/detailed.md` |
| Expert | Specialized audience, technical depth | `variants/expert.md` |

